Package: DGEobj.utils
Type:    Package
Title:   Differential Gene Expression (DGE) Analysis Plots
Version: 1.0.0.9005
Description:
    Provides a function toolkit to facilitate reproducible RNA-Seq DGE
    analysis.  The functions include workflow and mapping/unit conversion functions
    including: runEdgeRNorm to normalize counts, runVoom  to run limma voom and lmfit,
    runSVA for detrending unknown covariates, convertCounts to convert a counts
    matrix to CPM/TPM/FPKM, and more.
